Permian Corp said effective march 5 raised posted price crude oil 50 ct barrel .
The raise brought posted price West texas Intermediate 50 ct 17.00 dlrs barrel .
West Texas Sour also raised 50 ct 17.00 dlrs barrel .
A Permian spokesman said South Louisiana sweet posted price also raised 50 ct barrel 17.35 dlrs .
